---
import PageShell from '../../../../components/PageShell.astro';
import CTABox from '../../../../components/CTABox.astro';
import ComparisonTable from '../../../../components/ComparisonTable.astro';

const tocItems = [
  { id: 'overview', text: 'SafetyWing in Singapore', level: 2 },
  { id: 'plans-and-pricing', text: 'Plans and Pricing', level: 2 },
  { id: 'who-its-for', text: 'Who Should Choose SafetyWing', level: 2 },
];

const relatedLinks = [
  { title: 'Health Insurance in Singapore', href: '/countries/singapore/insurance' },
  { title: 'SafetyWing Review', href: '/providers/safetywing' },
  { title: 'SafetyWing vs Cigna', href: '/compare/safetywing-vs-cigna-global' },
];

const planColumns = [
  { key: 'plan', header: 'Plan' },
  { key: 'coverage', header: 'Coverage' },
  { key: 'price', header: 'Price' },
];

const planRows = [
  { plan: 'Nomad Insurance', coverage: 'Travel medical', price: '$45-55/mo' },
  { plan: 'Remote Health', coverage: 'Health insurance', price: '$160-220/mo' },
];
---

<PageShell
  title="SafetyWing in Singapore"
  description="Guide to using SafetyWing in Singapore. Budget nomad coverage limitations in Singapore's expensive healthcare market."
  headline="SafetyWing in Singapore"
  subheadline="Budget travel medical insurance—but is it enough for Singapore?"
  heroBackgroundImage="/images/countries/singapore-hero-bg.png"
  tocItems={tocItems}
  relatedLinks={relatedLinks}
  ctaButtonText="Get a SafetyWing Quote"
  ctaButtonHref="/go/safetywing"
>
  <h2 id="overview">SafetyWing in Singapore</h2>
  <p>
    SafetyWing is popular among digital nomads for affordable travel medical insurance. However, for Singapore residents, SafetyWing has significant limitations given the city-state's expensive healthcare environment.
  </p>

  <div class="bg-amber-50 border border-amber-200 rounded-lg p-4 my-6">
    <p class="text-amber-800 text-sm">
      <strong>Important:</strong> SafetyWing Nomad Insurance is travel medical insurance with a $250K limit. Given Singapore's high healthcare costs, this may be insufficient for serious medical events.
    </p>
  </div>

  <CTABox
    title="Need Comprehensive Coverage?"
    description="Consider proper health insurance for Singapore's expensive healthcare."
    buttonText="See Better Options"
    buttonHref="/go/safetywing"
    variant="highlight"
  />

  <h2 id="plans-and-pricing">Plans and Pricing</h2>

  <div class="my-8 border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg overflow-hidden">
    <ComparisonTable columns={planColumns} rows={planRows} />
  </div>

  <h3>Nomad Insurance Limitations</h3>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Coverage limit:</strong> $250K—may be insufficient for major procedures in Singapore</li>
    <li><strong>No outpatient coverage:</strong> Limited to emergency and acute care</li>
    <li><strong>Pre-existing conditions:</strong> Not covered</li>
    <li><strong>Mental health:</strong> Not covered</li>
    <li><strong>Routine care:</strong> Not covered</li>
  </ul>

  <h3>Remote Health Option</h3>
  <p>
    SafetyWing's Remote Health product is actual health insurance and more suitable for Singapore residents. However, verify coverage limits are adequate for Singapore's expensive private healthcare.
  </p>

  <h2 id="who-its-for">Who Should Choose SafetyWing in Singapore</h2>

  <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 my-8">
    <div class="bg-green-50 border border-green-200 rounded-lg p-6">
      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-green-900 mb-3">Potentially Suitable</h3>
      <ul class="space-y-2 text-green-800">
        <li>Short-term visitors (not residents)</li>
        <li>Digital nomads passing through</li>
        <li>Those with other primary coverage</li>
        <li>Remote Health users wanting basic coverage</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="bg-red-50 border border-red-200 rounded-lg p-6">
      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-red-900 mb-3">Not Recommended</h3>
      <ul class="space-y-2 text-red-800">
        <li>Singapore residents as primary coverage</li>
        <li>Those needing comprehensive coverage</li>
        <li>Anyone with pre-existing conditions</li>
        <li>Families requiring maternity coverage</li>
        <li>Expats using private hospitals</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>

  <p>
    For Singapore residents, we recommend proper international health insurance with adequate coverage limits. See our <a href="/countries/singapore/insurance">Singapore insurance guide</a> for better options.
  </p>

  <CTABox
    title="Need Better Singapore Coverage?"
    description="Compare comprehensive international health insurance plans."
    buttonText="See Recommended Plans"
    buttonHref="/go/safetywing"
    variant="highlight"
  />

  <div class="bg-neutral-50 border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg p-6 mt-8">
    <p class="text-sm text-neutral-600">
      <strong>Disclaimer:</strong> SafetyWing Nomad Insurance may not provide adequate coverage for Singapore's expensive healthcare. Consider comprehensive health insurance instead.
    </p>
  </div>
</PageShell>
